Class Win32IESettings

java.lang.Object
  com.btr.proxy.search.desktop.win.Win32IESettings

public class Win32IESettings
extends java.lang.Object

Proxy settings container used for the native methods. Will contain the Internet Explorer proxy settings as reported by windows WinHTTP API.

Author:
Bernd Rosstauscher (proxyvole@rosstauscher.de) Copyright 2009
